Data Visualisation Developer
Moscow.

Responsibility:
Develop customized dashboards and reports answering the needs of business.
Partner with BI dev team to develop new or modify existing data models.
Combine data from multiple sources using fastest, simplest and most productive way.

Requirements:
Proficiency in SQL: proven skills in data retrieval from multiple sources; deep knowledge of aggregation, window functions and SQL query optimization techniques; ability to read SQL execution plan and to write stored procedures and triggers.
Experience with BI technologies (i.e. Microstrategy, ClickView, Tableau, PowerBI and the like).

More info https://is.gd/bPcvB7
